data.description: Wonderful home in the heart of Prescott with views of Granite Dells and Willow Lake, Granite Mountain, and the San Francisco Peaks. If you're looking for a short commute to shopping, ERAU, hiking and biking trails, and Prescott's best dog park, look no further! New HVAC, new Anderson Windows, new exterior paint, new flooring, newer roof, upgraded kitchen, and new appliances. Front porch views of Granite Mountain, back patio views of Willow Lake, Mingus Mtn and the Dells all the way to SF Peaks. Huge living room and kitchen has tons of storage cabinets. Pet free and smoke free house. Fantastic low-maintenance, flat yard with possible RV parking. Exterior storage shed. Live on one level on a quiet street within 2 minutes of the Fry's shopping center. New leased solar system!
